{"tid":1810900,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明日上水反水貨集會遊行獲發不反對通知書","createTime":"2020-01-04T08:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T14:12:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70707f44ee8f3df8799714122a0833e1ca56aa33","tid":1810900,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1500997_1_L_20200104163418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1500997_1_L_20200104163418.jpg&h=887f83b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有北區區議員發起明日在上水集會遊行，要求正視水貨問題，下午1時半在上水花園第一號集會，2時半開始遊行。活動已獲發不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n活動申請人、北區區議員林子琼表示，活動由北區居民發起，希望政府正視區內水貨客問題。她又說臨近農曆年，是水貨客於北區活躍的高峰期，又認為水貨客並非旅客，而是即日來回，風雨不改地前來，未有因近期的社會情況而減少。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，遊行以和平形式進行，有約100名的糾察在場維持秩序，她認為水貨客知道有活動會避開，不擔心會出現「踢喼」或與水貨客衝突情況。另一名北區區議員陳旭明希望警方與遊行人士都要克制，避免出現混亂情況。"},{"pid":"4ebf4aa0a549d85825a79078865078ca8a06af0c","tid":1810900,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:54:14.000Z","msg":"不反對通知書 = 準備無差別濫捕"},{"pid":"ffa480dc33b5f62c1804aa05736b34e6fd76a037","tid":1810900,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b4aed07a80b00c984d806d918c7e0549fbd836","tid":1810900,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56afde832762effa0f40992a82ba586b63c47628","tid":1810900,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/